Sentencas: The formation of an oxide layer on different metallic samples (i.e., Crofer 22 APU, SS430 and Conicro 4023 W188) treated at 800 degrees C for 100 and 1000 h in air was investigated using X-ray diffraction (XRD).
Titulo: Oxide scale formation on different metallic interconnects for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: scanning electron microscopy (SEM/EDX) and thermogravimetric analysis.
Titulo: Oxide scale formation on different metallic interconnects for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The results indicate that the oxide scale formed on the metallic interconnect consists of a spinel (Fe, Cr, Mn)(3)O-4 or (Fe, Cr, Ni)(3)Co2O4 outer layer and a chromia (Cr2O3) inner layer.
Titulo: Oxide scale formation on different metallic interconnects for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The Crofer 22 APU and Conicro 4023 W188 samples were determined to be more promising as metallic interconnects than SS430 due to their higher oxidation resistance.
Titulo: Oxide scale formation on different metallic interconnects for solid oxide fuel cells
